name: Señor Culero Millonario Gold Frame
description:
“Meow Meow Meow. Meow Meow. Purr meow meow meow meow meow”

Translation: I am Señor Culero Millonario, and I’m a former housecat who turned into a major fatcat fascist asshole running the entire Kegalot Corporation and, as a result, basically this entire side of the country. We have our hands up everything. You think it’s weird for a cat to be running a multimillion-dollar corporation? Lemme just say that unlike you I ain’t no stinkin' pussy.

------


The Gallery Gehenna Project is a daily art project where there are multiple frames for each individual artwork, each with different levels of scarcity. Gold Frames are very limited with the lowest initial amount of any of the main 3 frame colors. All artworks will be compatible within the Gallery Gehenna Game where each NFT will unlock a story segment.
